<TEXT>
THOUSANDS of pounds have been collected lately for children in need; where are
these children? In a country where #90m is spent each week on lottery tickets?
Surely not!
Millions of children throughout the world have never tasted pure clear water.
There is something far wrong somewhere.
Jenny Boatman,
Brownhills, Beith.
