McKee (West of Scotland), Derek Stark (Boroughmuir); Mark McKenzie (Stirling
County), Gary Armstrong (Jed-Forest); Milan Brown (Melrose) Kevin Barrie
(Jed-Forest), Gordon McIlwham (Glasgow High/Kelvinside), Robbie Brown
(Melrose), John Jeffrey (Kelso), Murray Wallace (Glasgow High/Kelvinside),
