<TEXT>
Moschino
Cream crepe shift dress by Moschino Cheap &amp; Chic, #250 at Cruise, Ingram Street
and Princes Square, Glasgow; Corniche, Jeffrey Street, Edinburgh.
Prada
Chocolate brown patent handbag, #440 and black crepe dress, #500. Both by
Prada, exclusively in Scotland at Pollyanna, Glassford Street, Glasgow.
Givenchy
Pure silk headsquares by Givenchy, #69.95 at Jenners, Princes Street, Edinburgh.
Lacroix
Boucle knit suit, #364 from Bazar by Christian Lacroix at Corniche, Jeffrey
Street, Edinburgh.  Silk scarf by Christian Lacroix, #89 at Jenners, Princes
Street, Edinburgh.
Chanel
No 5 perfume by Chanel, from #53 (7ml bottle) at Frasers, Buchanan Street,
Glasgow; Debenhams, Argyle Street, Glasgow; Jenners, Princes Street, Edinburgh.
Hermes
Red leather envelope bag with monogram by Hermes, #555 at Frasers, Buchanan
Street, Glasgow. Black merino turtleneck, to order only.
Moschino
Felt flower and plexiglass necklace by Moschino Bijoux, #119 at Frasers,
Buchanan Street, Glasgow.
Valentino
Black lace-trimmed bra by Valentino, #25 and matching briefs, #18. Both at
Frasers, Buchanan Street, Glasgow. Boxed nightshirt with embroidered namestyle
